<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<text id="02-output-contract" title="PM + Tech-Lead Grooming Agenda Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema (draft-07) for the checklist artefact this methodology produces. The validator script enforces required keys, evidence-link presence, and slug match. Forbidden patterns: missing evidence array, slug mismatch, free-form version strings.</summary>

  <section title="Schema">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/pm-tech-lead-grooming-agenda.json",
  "title": "PM + Tech-Lead Grooming Agenda",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "slug",
    "version",
    "owner",
    "produced_at",
    "evidence",
    "body"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "slug": {
      "type": "string",
      "const": "pm-tech-lead-grooming-agenda"
    },
    "version": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$"
    },
    "owner": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 2
    },
    "produced_at": {
      "type": "string",
      "format": "date-time"
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "type": "string",
        "format": "uri-reference"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "body": {
      "type": "object"
    },
    "ai_drafted": {
      "type": "boolean"
    },
    "reviewer": {
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "slug": "pm-tech-lead-grooming-agenda",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "owner": "tech-lead@example.com",
  "produced_at": "2026-05-22T12:00:00Z",
  "evidence": [
    "https://example.com/adr/0007",
    "./docs/decision-log.md#2026-05-22"
  ],
  "body": {
    "summary": "real content here"
  },
  "ai_drafted": false,
  "reviewer": "tech-lead@example.com"
}
]]></code>
    <note>Required fields present, slug matches, evidence non-empty, version is semver.</note>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "slug": "wrong-slug",
  "version": "v1",
  "evidence": []
}
]]></code>
    <note>Slug mismatched, version not semver, evidence empty, body + owner + produced_at missing. Forbidden patterns: missing required keys, evidence=[], non-semver version, slug != expected.</note>
  </example>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-pm-tech-lead-grooming-agenda.py">Validator script (stdlib only, supports --self-test).</reference>
</text>
